    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DATA ENTRY -->
  <h2 class="sec">Data Entry &amp; Settings<span class="rule"></span></h2>
  <p class="sec-note">Entries persist in this dashboard's local storage. The daily refresh task overwrites connector-sourced values; active-member counts you enter here are preserved. Meta/Nextdoor values are re-baked by the weekly pull, so a mid-week manual correction there lasts until the next bake.</p>
